{"tid":312100,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 完全免費末日生存手機遊戲：Mini DAYZ","createTime":"2017-07-07T06:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T13:17:01.000Z","uid":7371,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e164653524456ca6a22f1708977ffddf31b9793","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://minidayz.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminidayz.com&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=128aa139\" target=\"_blank\">https://minidayz.com</a><br />\n官網有iOS/An版dl link<br />\n<br />\nGameplay Trailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYp_ESz2R9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYp_ESz2R9s&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f5248bc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYp_ESz2R9s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/144956_3a604ad7b01ba7bb9cfdad346a3f87db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F144956_3a604ad7b01ba7bb9cfdad346a3f87db.jpg&h=eb0337b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2D版手機版DAYZ<br />\ntown down視點唔會頭暈<br />\npixel art畫風只得幾十MB容量<br />\n免費冇IAP<br />\n認真係業界良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用官網字句：<br />\n<br />\nNO RULES, EXCEPT ONE:<br />\nTO SURVIVE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf96a2f9e9481390c87276c9fb71fa52ea74c65","tid":312100,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"好講技術<br />\n成日要走佬<br />\n埋身出血就等死<br />\n幾好玩<br />\n幫你推推"},{"pid":"ddc1ab1fce5e081f5bd6ea52130f0c77d0d26761","tid":312100,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"單機定可以一齊玩？"},{"pid":"e07383f9fc2956788ca332c1f1713c0f0722d9a2","tid":312100,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:37:50.000Z","msg":"有網頁版"},{"pid":"f61f7f5ad840004d18ad2c4a1f55e4b35b0d2f3f","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單機定可以一齊玩？</blockquote><br />\n單機<br />\n但開放世界求生玩法又隨機地圖<br />\n其實都好襟玩<br />\n<br />\n網頁版可連線同揸車"},{"pid":"3423a5da771e5a0955e7e3474de0b573aa2e5c9e","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"玩完個教學<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n<br />\n個教學同操作都好簡單易上手<br />\n右邊Button有圖示又適當時候會變<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/183755_d0ac19879df7fc0a4a0bd4c8a18f2559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F183755_d0ac19879df7fc0a4a0bd4c8a18f2559.jpg&h=c5a1490c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入屋會zoom in易睇D<br />\n<br />\n自動埋身打同開槍描準<br />\n多敵人時唔會操作混亂<br />\n手機game戰鬥簡單操作好重要<br />\n<br />\n有Perk用經驗值黎換<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/183726_52e0d250767100a3d5f95f2adb9971d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F183726_52e0d250767100a3d5f95f2adb9971d6.jpg&h=bce49407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n<br />\n左菇唔係浮動係fix位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至少玩完教學會想玩落去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/183707_a3263112afd6eef63e2cb69a632956f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F183707_a3263112afd6eef63e2cb69a632956f4.jpg&h=98a9120f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時唯一見到個廣告<br />\n只係主menu有個banner連去同公司另一隻game<br />\n其實都唔知佢賺到幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n教學個結局真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a173b329b45b55c37b8a71cb10842f839f832e","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好講技術<br />\n成日要走佬<br />\n埋身出血就等死<br />\n幾好玩<br />\n幫你推推</blockquote><br />\n要走佬都好呀<br />\n末日應該多危機<br />\n如果不停開槍駁火就係COD/L4D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf131f028cc7fed1e0e3dc4a1b88cc41f3ec627","tid":312100,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好講技術<br />\n成日要走佬<br />\n埋身出血就等死<br />\n幾好玩<br />\n幫你推推</blockquote><br />\n要走佬都好呀<br />\n末日應該多危機<br />\n如果不停開槍駁火就係COD/L4D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無槍係手既時候死得好快<br />\n有見到人?NPC? 拖住班怪圍死佢之後執左啲垃圾裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e9476f70f907f0b023e0b503b06fd16ba39536","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好講技術<br />\n成日要走佬<br />\n埋身出血就等死<br />\n幾好玩<br />\n幫你推推</blockquote><br />\n要走佬都好呀<br />\n末日應該多危機<br />\n如果不停開槍駁火就係COD/L4D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無槍係手既時候死得好快<br />\n有見到人?NPC? 拖住班怪圍死佢之後執左啲垃圾裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難玩<br />\n頭先玩到搵唔到食物死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8588822fe96280d1446c8437523589b4c679c80c","tid":312100,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"有網頁版開SER一齊玩?"},{"pid":"d77ad35124c68a28bff4101cb644a2fbc4336ac0","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/220106_17b4676e2c7bc4eb4b329dbafa62f5b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F220106_17b4676e2c7bc4eb4b329dbafa62f5b7.jpg&h=41ee194d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來左上角降傘圖襟佢有得睇廣告出個救援箱<br />\n但我試過只係普通食物<br />\n要等好耐先用到下次<br />\n所以其實都無乜用<br />\n個廣告只係連去開發者另一隻game"},{"pid":"cdb23457cd6b13b09b84d10153a347b184d122a5","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"主畫面設定可set支菇位置<br />\n<br />\n關game再入主menu有得continue"},{"pid":"791e6ef62ededc5c2296cf886e292eefb1905c84","tid":312100,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主畫面設定可set支菇位置<br />\n<br />\n關game再入主menu有得continue</blockquote><br />\n有冇玩網頁版?"},{"pid":"34304de79f60718263edfa248f2efa2f47d9c4b7","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/004706_1306b46e9ec140501dd0589e166b1148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F004706_1306b46e9ec140501dd0589e166b1148.jpg&h=4efe73d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係殺敵多定死得多<br />\n會慢慢解多左角色用<br />\n會多D起始裝備或perk"},{"pid":"55f55d0e04672851ba69d2ecb0651825d9618f40","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主畫面設定可set支菇位置<br />\n<br />\n關game再入主menu有得continue</blockquote><br />\n有冇玩網頁版?</blockquote><br />\n手機版單機都未玩掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b752f4ac179d139bad8f2254ff6f5034ba6a663","tid":312100,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"廢到仆街<br />\n我記得以前屋出面都會有野執<br />\n而家要入屋仲要少資源到仆街"},{"pid":"e75a7475c9fd8d869a814b350519d59828c0ad42","tid":312100,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"網頁版 <a href=\"https://minidayz.com/play/mp/\" data-sr-url=\"ht