mal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真心幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5cfa0e93afb298962ccb023962940d7033e9d9","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好少資源<br />\n有槍有彈就冇食物<br />\n有食物就冇武器<br />\n成日流血流死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真心幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n流血只流一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n飲品有時好少<br />\n止血道具極少<br />\n<br />\nD狗好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706849b6ec272ca1601a1927a7871eb4975726ce","tid":312100,"uid":30037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好少資源<br />\n有槍有彈就冇食物<br />\n有食物就冇武器<br />\n成日流血流死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真心幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n流血只流一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n飲品有時好少<br />\n止血道具極少<br />\n<br />\nD狗好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狗係好朋友黎 會咬zombie <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad40c9ea20400de43bc5ac0ab930355ec02921b5","tid":312100,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好少資源<br />\n有槍有彈就冇食物<br />\n有食物就冇武器<br />\n成日流血流死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真心幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n流血只流一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n飲品有時好少<br />\n止血道具極少<br />\n<br />\nD狗好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狗係好朋友黎 會咬zombie <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但試過水井飲水<br />\n三隻狗衝埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇喪屍<br />\n咁就死左"}]}